pro_course_detail.description:
Hello, my dear prospective students! 

I offer the Russian language from the scratch to a more advanced level for fluent communication with the Russian speakers and getting aquainted with the unique Russian culture, history and mentality. I have got a big variety of textbooks, readers, an amazing collection of educational videos, cartoons, popular movies with Russian or English subtitles and different online sources. And of course my enthusiasm and  experience in teaching. In other words there's everything to satisfy any student's needs and interests. What is required from you is just your time and efforts to be a success!

I can offer several courses:

Introduction Course / A1 Level:
- Russian alphabet;
- pronunciation of Russian sounds, intonation, phonetical rules;
- reading and writing exercises;
- basic grammar structures;
- basic conversations and every day topics;
- reading short stories;
- watching cartoons and movies with Russian and English captions;
- winging songs in karaoke and so on.

Grammar Course:
- parts of speech; 
- genders;
- cases; 
 - conjugation of verbs in different Tenses;
 - Imperative Mood;
- question forms and so on.

Elementary - Advanced Course / A2 – C1:
- discussions of books, movies and everyday issues; 
- studying culture and history of Russia;
- writing essays;
- mastering the grammar and lexics.

If you are interested in my offer and curious to learn our "mysterious Russian soul", do not hesitate to fill in my teacher's form, write a message to me with more details, your wishes and expectations from the course. And do not miss a boat to book a trial lesson with me :) See you soon!

Have a great day!

Best regards, Catherine
